title: American Idol Phillip Phillips Weds Longtime Girlfriend - Foster's Daily Democrat
text:
Phillips, who won Season 11 of the singing competition, and Blackwell tied the knot Saturday evening at the Resora Plantation in Atlanta, Ga. About 250 guests attended the wedding.
